summary:
The Security Council,

Recalling resolutions 1958 (2010) and 2335 (2016),

Acknowledging the final report of the Secretary-General (S/2017/820),

1. Welcomes implementing arrangements between the Secretary-General and Iraq as per resolution 1958 (2010) paragraph 7;

2. Welcomes transfer of remaining escrow account funds to Iraq's Government as per resolution 2335 (2016);

3. Concludes that measures imposed by resolutions 1958 (2010) and 2335 (2016) under Chapter VII have been fully implemented.
